      "props": {
        "text": "Backend pattern compounds: new `_build_gallery_card_payload()` is the sibling of PR #42's `_build_embed_summary_payload()` — cheap reads over the per-simulation on-disk layout (state/config/quality/trajectory/resolution JSON), graceful per-sim degradation, no DB joins. GET /api/simulation/public is paginated, sorted created_at desc, with a 30s public cache.",
        "variant": "body"
